<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root { --primary-color: <%= branding.primaryColor || '#0ea5e9' %>; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f9ff; min-height: 100vh; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
    .consent-card { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .consent-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #0284c7); color: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0; text-align: center; }
    .consent-body { padding: 2rem; }
    .info-box { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .warning-box { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--primary-color); border-color: var(--primary-color); padding: 0.75rem 2rem; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #0284c7; }
    .checkbox-large { width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem; margin-right: 0.75rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="consent-card">
    <div class="consent-header">
      <i class="bi bi-shield-check" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
      <h1 class="h3 mb-1">Parental Consent Required</h1>
      <p class="mb-0">Your approval is needed before your child can use TutorAI</p>
    </div>

    <div class="consent-body">
      <p>Dear <%= consent.parentFirstName %>,</p>

      <p>
        <strong><%= student.firstName %> <%= student.lastName %></strong> (age <%= consent.childAge %>)
        has requested to create an account on TutorAI, our AI-powered educational tutoring platform.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h5><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>What TutorAI Does</h5>
        <ul class="mb-0">
          <li>Provides AI-powered tutoring in 74+ subjects (K-12)</li>
          <li>Tracks learning progress and quiz performance</li>
          <li>Allows voice and text interaction with AI tutors</li>
          <li>Stores session history and educational achievements</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <h5><i class="bi bi-database me-2"></i>Information We Collect</h5>
        <ul class="mb-0">
          <li>Name and email address</li>
          <li>Date of birth (for age-appropriate content)</li>
          <li>Learning progress, quiz answers, and grades</li>
          <li>Messages and questions sent to AI tutors</li>
          <li>Session timing and usage patterns</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0"><strong>We do NOT sell personal information or share it with third parties for marketing.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <form method="POST" action="<%= typeof basePath !== 'undefined' ? basePath : '' %>/coppa/verify">
        <input type="hidden" name="token" value="<%= token %>">

        <div class="form-check mb-4">
          <input class="form-check-input checkbox-large" type="checkbox" name="agree" id="agree" value="1" required>
          <label class="form-check-label" for="agree">
            I am the parent or legal guardian of <%= student.firstName %>, and I give my consent for them to use TutorAI and for the collection of their data as described above.
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex gap-3">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary flex-grow-1">
            <i class="bi bi-check-lg me-2"></i>I Give My Consent
          </button>
          <a href="<%= typeof basePath !== 'undefined' ? basePath : '' %>/coppa/reject?token=<%= token %>" class="btn btn-outline-danger">
            Decline
          </a>
        </div>
      </form>

      <hr class="my-4">

      <p class="text-muted small">
        <strong>Your Rights:</strong> Under COPPA, you have the right to review your child's personal information,
        request its deletion, and revoke consent at any time. Contact us at support@tutorai.com for any questions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
